title: ** 174 KNICKERBOCKER ** 2 Bed / 1.5 Bath!
posting_body: ["One month's broker fee", 'September 1st move in date', 'Text Lihi @ 3477484234 w/ address 174 Knickerbocker', 'Modern renovated 3 bed/1.5 baths located on Knickerbocker Ave and Melrose St, near the Jefferson & Morgan L Trains, near the M Train Knickerbocker or Central Ave, short walk to the Myrtle Broadway J, M, Z EXPRESS TRAIN, only a 17 minute train ride into NYC!', '– in a rapidly evolving part of the East Williamsburg / Bushwick area, All Restaurants, Cafes, Bars right nearby, 1 block from Maria Hernandez Park, huge supermarket at the corner! -', 'Some of the staples around the neighborhood are: The Cobra Club, Cafe Ghia, Arepera Guacuco, House Of Yes, Maria Hernandez Park, and much much … Modern kitchen with stainless steal kitchen appliances and island breakfast bar Spacious bedrooms with great windows and large closets 1.5 bathrooms with tub and shower Central Air and Heat Hardwood flooring High ceiling Video intercom system Guarantors Accepted Pets allowed *Upon approval.', 'Roof Deck / rooftop access Laundry in the building Showing by appointment – 1 Months broker fee due at signing']
